title: Population of Saba ( Caribbean Netherlands ) 2011 to 2019
summary: In general Number of people has rose over the Year.
Number of people is roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, and lastly slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Number of people, of value 1947.0 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Number of people, of value 1811.0 was reported at Year 2015
